OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F163A1782573492
OL,1,Wj5hw1~{4k7juhw1{$             G2/2
OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GUK long range forecast
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sun 12 Jul to Sun 26 Jul
OL,6,FHigh pressure is looking slightly more
OL,7,Flikely than low pressure during the
OL,8,Fearly part of this period, meaning a
OL,9,Fgreater chance of settled and drier
OL,10,Fthan average conditions. Outbreaks of
OL,11,Frain and stronger are possible at
OL,12,Ftimes, these more likely further
OL,13,Fnorth. As normal for the time of year,
OL,14,Fthere is still a chance of some heavy
OL,15,Fand thundery showers which may
OL,16,Finterrupt any warm and settled
OL,17,Fweather. Towards the end of July there
OL,18,Fis no reliable signal for preferring
OL,19,Fany one weather pattern over another.
OL,20,FHowever, temperatures are likely to be
OL,21,Fabove normal on the whole, with a
OL,22,Fgreater than normal chance of hot
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,23,Fconditions developing at times.
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
